  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/c576a3f9b88512911c6b9ed12da0bd74.poster.avif?t=1771311161\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/c576a3f9b88512911c6b9ed12da0bd74.webm?t=1771311161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/c576a3f9b88512911c6b9ed12da0bd74.mp4?t=1771311161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/0784b9202382c3ae5b138d7a9c04d37e.avif?t=1771311161\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>Battlethorne Survivors is a third person action roguelite survival game with a focus on companions. Massacre hordes of fantastical beasts and collect gold for unlocking powerful trinkets to take on even harder maps and Bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/e08a5f7f942cb676c1d2210a493c2ff5.avif?t=1771311161\" width=616 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight thousands of fantastical beasts<br></li><li>Over 20 Unique enemy types with their own unique attacks<br></li><li>Over 30 Companions to Unlock<br></li><li>Unlock hundreds of trinkets to power up your character<br></li><li>6 maps with 12 Difficulty tiers<br></li><li>Choose from 18 characters<br></li><li>5 Bosses to defeat</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746340/extras/0784b9202382c3ae5b138d7a9c04d37e.avif?t=1771311161\" width=616 height=64 /></span>",
